thread.title: Data Respons Q3 EBITDA rises to NOK 14.7 million
thread.title_full: BRIEF-Data Respons Q3 EBITDA rises to NOK 14.7 million | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: Data Respons Q3 EBITDA rises to NOK 14.7 million
text:
Oct 15 Data Respons ASA :
* Q3 operating revenue was 226 million Norwegian crowns ($28.1 million) versus 186 million crowns year ago, a growth of 21 pct
* Q3 EBITDA 14.7 million crowns versus 12.3 million crowns year ago
* Order intake for Q3 was 177 million crowns versus 162 million crowns year ago Source text for Eikon:
 ($1 = 8.0385 Norwegian crowns) (Gdynia Newsroom)
